Package: QCnormSE
Type: Package
Title: Quality Control of Normalized Gene Expression Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Silke", "Szymczak", email = "szymczak@medinfo.uni-kiel.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of several quality control procedures and processing 
    steps for normalized gene expression data sets from microarray and RNA-seq
    experiments in a common framework. It heavily builds upon existing CRAN and
    Bioconductor packages.
